hgst  wikipedia hgst from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from hitachi global storage technologies jump to navigation search hitachi global storage technologies redirects here it is not to be confused with hitachi data systems this article relies too much on references to primary sources please improve this by adding secondary or tertiary sources february  learn how and when to remove this template message hgst inc type subsidiary of western digital industry computer storage devices predecessor hitachi global storage technologies founded   years ago  headquarters san jose california united states area served worldwide key people mike cordano president products hard disk drives solidstate drives external storage devices number of employees  parent hitachi ltd – western digital –present website wwwhgstcom hgst inc formerly hitachi global storage technologies is a wholly owned subsidiary of western digital that sells hard disk drives solidstate drives and external storage products and services contents  history  products  hard drives and solidstate drives  external storage  see also  references  external links historyedit hitachi global storage technologies was founded on january   as a merger of the hard disk drive businesses of ibm and hitachi hitachi paid ibm us billion for its hdd business on march   western digital wd acquired hitachi global storage technologies for  billion in cash and  million shares of wd common stock valued at approximately  billion the deal resulted in hitachi ltd owning approximately  percent of wd shares outstanding and reserving the right to designate two individuals to the board of directors of wd it was agreed that wd would operate with wd technologies and hgst as wholly owned subsidiaries and they would compete in the marketplace with separate brands and product lines in may  wd divested to toshiba assets that enabled toshiba to manufacture and sell inch hard drives for the desktop and consumer electronics markets to address the requirements of regulatory agencies hitachi global storage technologies japan ltd is the japanese branch of hitachi global storage technologies inc in november  the company announced a  tb capacity drive filled with helium in september  the company announced a  tb helium drive which uses shingled magnetic recording to improve density on october   western digital corporation announced a decision from chinas ministry of commerce mofcom which enabled the company to integrate substantial portions of its hgst and wd subsidiaries under western digital corporation western digital but they must offer both hgst and wd product brands in the market and maintain separate sales teams for two years from the date of the decision as such as of october   hgst is a western digital brand and no longer a separate entity productsedit hard drives and solidstate drivesedit ultrastar huaala ultrastar – enterpriseclass line of inch and inch hdds with scsi fibre channel sas and sata interfaces and a line of inch and inch fibre channel and sas ssds deskstar – desktopclass line in inch form factor with sata interfaces travelstar – mobileclass line in inch form factor with sata interfaces endurastar – ruggedized line in inch form factor with pata or sata interfaces primarily for automotive applications cinemastar – inch and inch form factors optimized for consumer electronics applications requiring quiet operation and streaming support external storageedit lifestudio products announced in  but now discontinued were external hard drives that combine photo organization software a d wall for displaying content a connected usb flash key gtechnology external storage products acquired in  are sold to apple macintosh communities including users of multimedia content such as final cut pro digital audiovideo production professionals touro family of cloud storage backup products see alsoedit hitachilg data storage hlds – joint venture of hitachi and lg manufacturer of dvd and bluray drives hitachi data systems hds – manufacturer of modular enterprise storage systems software and services referencesedit  archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    hitachi establishes hitachi global storage technologies taking a bold new step for storage innovation press release hitachi january     hitachi buys ibm disk drive business june   archived march   at the wayback machine  hitachi and ibm complete hard disk drive agreement press release ibm december     hitachi completes transfer of hard disk drive business to western digital press release hitachi canada march     wd completes acquisition of hitachi global storage technologies  creates the industrys deepest technology capability and broadest product portfolio press release western digital march     byford sam march   western digital completes b hitachi gst buyout becomes worlds largest hdd manufacturer the verge   wd reaches agreement with toshiba corporation to divest certain inch hdd assets press release western digital february     wd completes divestiture of assets to toshiba corporation press release western digital may     mellor chris november   heliumfilled disks lift off you cant keep these tb beasts down the register retrieved november     gasior geoff september   shingled platters breathe helium inside hgsts tb hard drive the tech report retrieved september     western digital corporation announces decision from china’s ministry of commerce enabling integration of substantial portions of hgst and wd subsidiaries press release western digital october     paul alcorn  mofcom approves hgst wd integration with two year hold separate clause tomsitprocom retrieved    china finally says yes to wdhgst union theregistercouk retrieved    dong ngo july   hitachi unveils lifestudio storage solutions cnet news blog retrieved june     hitachi gst completes acquisition of fabrik inc — company sets stage for continued global expansion pdf news release april   archived from the original pdf on september   retrieved june    external linksedit official website グローバルストレージテクノロジーズ in japanese hitachi establishes hitachi global storage technologies taking a bold new step for storage innovation hitachi ltd press release v t e hitachi divisions and subsidiaries current clarion hitachi cable hitachi cable manchester hitachi canadian industries hitachi capital hitachi construction machinery hitachi construction machinery europe hitachi consulting hitachi data systems bluearc hitachi electronics hitachi maxell hitachi medical systems hitachi rail horizon nuclear power jecs former euclid trucks fabrik hitachi global storage technologies joint ventures and shareholdings agility trains  alaxala networks  ge hitachi nuclear energy  hitachilg data storage japan display  nec casio mobile communications  nippon columbia  renesas electronics  telcon construction solutions  products services and standards current alis dvhs emiew hitachi adaptable modular storage  hitachi dx hitachi starboard locomotives hitachi magic wand multiple units hitachi  hitachi sr hitachi travelstar hitachi truecopy lsr m stacked volumetric optical disk superh universal storage platform defunct h family hd hitac hitac s hitachi  hitachi deskstar hitachi flora prius hitachi g hitachi hatsukaze hitachi sr hitachi t hitachi tr m microdrive people namihei odaira kenichi ohmae hiroaki nakanishi takashi kawamura places hitachi kashiwa soccer stadium hitachi ibaraki hitachi tower tsūtenkaku other dkb group hdmi licensing hitachi tours championship hitachi data systems history the hitachi foundation hindu hitachi scholarships hitachi sunrockers hitachi rivale kashiwa reysol now integrated into other hitachi divisions or business groupings sold category commons v t e hard disk drive manufacturers history of hard disk drives present seagate technology toshiba western digital hgst past computer memories inc conner peripherals control data corporation digital equipment corporation excelstor technology fujitsu hewlettpackard ibm