s endurastar – ruggedized line in inch form factor with pata or sata interfaces primarily for automotive applications cinemastar – inch and inch form factors optimized for consumer electronics applications requiring quiet operation and streaming support external storageedit lifestudio products announced in  but now discontinued were external hard drives that combine photo organization software a d wall for displaying content a connected usb flash key gtechnology external storage products acquired in  are sold to apple macintosh communities including users of multimedia content such as final cut pro digital audiovideo production professionals touro family of cloud storage backup products see alsoedit hitachilg data storage hlds – joint venture of hitachi and lg manufacturer of dvd and bluray drives hitachi data systems hds – manufacturer of modular enterprise storage systems software and services referencesedit  archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    hitachi establishes hitachi global storage technologies taking a bold new step for storage innovation press release hitachi january     hitachi buys ibm disk drive business june   archived march   at the wayback machine  hitachi and ibm complete hard disk drive agreement press release ibm december     hitachi completes transfer of hard disk drive business to western digital press release hitachi canada march     wd completes acquisition of hitachi global storage technologies  creates the industrys deepest technology capability and broadest product portfolio press release western digital march     byford sam march   western digital completes b hitachi gst buyout becomes worlds largest hdd manufacturer the verge   wd reaches agreement with toshiba corporation to divest certain inch hdd assets press release western digital february     wd completes divestiture of assets to toshiba corporation press release western digital may     mellor chris november   heliumfilled disks lift off you cant keep these tb b