ed in hitachi ltd owning approximately  percent of wd shares outstanding and reserving the right to designate two individuals to the board of directors of wd it was agreed that wd would operate with wd technologies and hgst as wholly owned subsidiaries and they would compete in the marketplace with separate brands and product lines in may  wd divested to toshiba assets that enabled toshiba to manufacture and sell inch hard drives for the desktop and consumer electronics markets to address the requirements of regulatory agencies hitachi global storage technologies japan ltd is the japanese branch of hitachi global storage technologies inc in november  the company announced a  tb capacity drive filled with helium in september  the company announced a  tb helium drive which uses shingled magnetic recording to improve density on october   western digital corporation announced a decision from chinas ministry of commerce mofcom which enabled the company to integrate substantial portions of its hgst and wd subsidiaries under western digital corporation western digital but they must offer both hgst and wd product brands in the market and maintain separate sales teams for two years from the date of the decision as such as of october   hgst is a western digital brand and no longer a separate entity productsedit hard drives and solidstate drivesedit ultrastar huaala ultrastar – enterpriseclass line of inch and inch hdds with scsi fibre channel sas and sata interfaces and a line of inch and inch fibre channel and sas ssds deskstar – desktopclass line in inch form factor with sata interfaces travelstar – mobileclass line in inch form factor with sata interfaces endurastar – ruggedized line in inch form factor with pata or sata interfaces primarily for automotive applications cinemastar – inch and inch form factors optimized for consumer electronics applications requiring quiet operation and streaming support external storageedit lifestudio products announced in  but now discontinued were external hard drives that combine photo organization software a d wall for displaying content a connected usb flash key gtechnology external storage products acquired in  are sold to apple macintosh communities including users of multimedia content such as final cut pro digital audiovideo production professionals touro family of cloud storage backup products see alsoedit hitachilg data storage hlds – joint venture of hitachi and lg manufacturer of dvd and bluray drives hitachi data systems hds – manufacturer of modular enterprise storage systems software and services referencesedit  archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    hitachi establishes hitachi global storage technologies taking a bold new step for storage innovation press release hitachi january     hitachi buys ibm disk drive business june   archived march   at the wayback machine  hitachi and ibm complete hard disk drive agreement press release ibm december     hitachi completes transfer of hard disk drive business to western digital press release hitachi canada march     wd completes acquisition of hitachi global storage technologies  creates the industrys deepest technology capability and broadest product portfolio press release western digital march     byford sam march   western digital completes b hitachi gst buyout becomes worlds largest hdd manufacturer the verge   wd reaches agreement with toshiba corporation to divest certain inch hdd assets press release western digital february     wd completes divestiture of assets to toshiba corporation press release western digital may     mellor chris november   heliumfilled disks lift off you cant keep these tb beasts down the register retrieved november     gasior geoff september   shingled platters breathe helium inside hgsts tb hard drive the tech report retrieved september     western digital corporation announces decision from china’s ministry of commerce enabling integration of substantial portions of hgst and wd subsidiaries