iews if contacted for an onsite interview you will be contacted to complete any additional required information along with instructions step  evaluation after we have completed interviews we’ll determine the top candidate for the job and make an offer step  preemployment screening preemployment screening will be conducted based upon the position requirements step  employment after successfully completing the preemployment screening you will be ready to join our team if you haven’t been selected we will let you know the position has been filled keep in touch online so you will know about future opportunities step  congratulations you’re hired careers disability if you are interested in applying for employment and need special assistance or an accommodation to use our website or to apply for a position please send an email with your request to hiremehgstcom we evaluate requests for reasonable accommodation on a casebycase basis linkedin twitter hgst blog youtube facebook productshard drives solidstate drives platforms systems affiliate brandstouro external storage touro cloud backup solutionsby use casebackup recovery  archive private  hybrid clouds database acceleration virtualization by industrycloud service providers financial services healthcare  life sciences oil  gas telecommunications media  entertainment other enterprise data centers supporthard drive support solidstate drive support software support systems support platforms support product security partnerspartners first program enterprise partner program partner alliance companycompany info executive team careers corporate citizenship global footprint investor relations innovation center resources public relationsmedia room press releases news and reviews events and webinars blog   hgst inc site map trademarks privacy policy legal policy cookie policy hgst inc  revenue and financial reports  db hoovers menu buy reports  lists how it works united states united kingdom   login company people industry search d